{"tid":759663,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"二萬人報名爭去恐怖莊園　玩完身心受創屬於正常？","createTime":"2018-07-28T22:52:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-29T12:54:04.000Z","uid":28366,"like":5,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"994aca522ee7c6a7ffa7067e2f96b5bd5740c8be","tid":759663,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T22:52:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/29/064728_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F29%2F064728_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg&h=45663e99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔少去外地旅遊時，都會參與當地的local tour， Netflix節目《Dark Tourist》(非一般旅程)主持David Farrier就分別在日本、美國參與了不同的遊行團，其中在荷里活一站，更去到有全世界最恐怖鬼屋美譽嘅McKamey恐怖莊園。<br />\n<br />\n恐怖莊園由電影狂熱粉Russ同女友Carol以50萬美元打造，入場費係零，但每位參加者都要簽下一份長達45頁的生死狀。由於玩晒成個恐怖莊園需時5小時以上，加上每次只能有二人進入，所以至今排隊輪侯人數有近2萬多人&hellip;到底呢個恐怖莊園有乜吸引之處呢？主持人David簽下生死狀之後，隨將被封箱膠紙朦眼、口部塞入一個類似牙醫檢查時會用上的擴大器（作用係令人流口水）、束身衣外再加上尿片，負責人Russ之後再為David戴耳機，強迫佢聽一啲令人情緒不安的配樂。不過，原來呢個只係熱身，但David就已經話頂唔順，Russ再三問是否決定要退出，並表示作出呢個決定會遭到耿笑，David話:「我不喜歡這件事，整個情況都很可怕，我不喜歡，我懦弱無用，不敢參加McKamey恐怖莊園，我退出了。」David脫身之後，情緒略為激動，亦表示唔明白點解會有人參加恐怖莊園。<br />\n<br />\n其實恐怖莊園開業至今16年，都未曾有人完成過整個「旅程」，有曾入內的參加者透露會經歷鎖鏈囚禁、被逼食臭雞蛋，<span style=\"color: red;\">與蛇或蜘蛛困在密室</span>等等過程，亦有參加者因身心受創而告上法庭，指除被拷打、虐待之外，更慘遭水刑，令人有快要淹死的感覺。但負責人Russ就以「皮肉傷和心理上的恐懼是不能避免，但不會遭受到生命的威脅。」作為反駁。Russ在接受David訪問時，指恐怖莊園由於費用全免，所以收入多數都係靠捐款，並指在屋鬼作使出的虐待招式，基本上是在軍隊中學習。他更指恐怖莊園最近才搬到Summertown，但就收到有關方面的「終止營業」的命令，原因是該區區民不想有疑似的殺人犯存在。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/29/065009_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F29%2F065009_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg&h=1f36d6e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/29/065011_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F29%2F065011_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg&h=51be14af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/29/065013_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F29%2F065013_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg&h=c8bc1b32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/29/065015_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F29%2F065015_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg&h=b8cb0dd4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/29/065016_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F29%2F065016_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg&h=80f086a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/29/065018_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F29%2F065018_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg&h=f91ca4f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/29/065019_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F29%2F065019_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg&h=58252018&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/29/065021_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F29%2F065021_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg&h=988a0fa2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/29/065023_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F29%2F065023_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg&h=0188003f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/29/065024_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F29%2F065024_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg&h=d0c69237&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/29/065032_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F29%2F065032_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg&h=e7a2722a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1627e92afdde1fc7da803c598c01e10c7a0638ab","tid":759663,"uid":66943,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T23:14:18.000Z","msg":"打你老母造"},{"pid":"2708665ac942b2c9cbf20ed42ad03fc048c997d5","tid":759663,"uid":189109,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T23:17:54.000Z","msg":"恐怖得過俄羅斯練膽大法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?"},{"pid":"1a7466375846de78d286e7a69e0308c265ac3e27","tid":759663,"uid":26773,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T23:21:36.000Z","msg":"張張死圖"},{"pid":"f31d39b1e12bbe4d413c793a71fc069b44067140","tid":759663,"uid":130901,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T23:22:05.000Z","msg":"排隊入去比人虐待<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fc8027d852a70a0e8690d9051ba99befcd7649e","tid":759663,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T23:28:43.000Z","msg":"XXXXXXXXXX"},{"pid":"1c1eb2f32ac48f414c902aa8c53d8877029a48a1","tid":759663,"uid":73340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T00:21:50.000Z","msg":"恐怖莊園最恐怖係淨靠捐款又唔會賺錢但又可以生存咁耐"},{"pid":"aeab42c730419c29f4dacf52a2